OL,5, The PM's closest aide Mark Fullbrook is
OL,6, not paid directly by the government -  
OL,7, but instead gets his salary via a      
OL,8, private firm, it has emerged.          
OL,10,FOpposition parties have described the  
OL,11,Farrangement as "shocking" and called   
OL,12,Ffor an urgent investigation into       
OL,13,Fpossible conflicts of interest.        
OL,15,FLiz Truss appointed Mr Fullbrook as her
OL,16,Fchief of staff earlier this month.     
OL,18,FHis salary is reported to be paid via  
OL,19,Fhis own lobbying firm Fullbrook        
OL,20,FStrategies, which was set up in March. 
